"{\"uid\": \"miragenews.com-olympic-climate-criticism-demands-clear-1294938\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Opinion piece by Christine Nellemann, Dean of Sustainability, Diversity and International Cooperation at DTU.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.058459556769559e-14, \"text\": \"Christine\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Blair\"}, {\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999969175412148, \"rank\": 2.2173570225270873e-06, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Opinion piece\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"Sustainability\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 60}, {\"ngram\": \"Diversity\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"International Cooperation\", \"from\": 76, \"to\": 101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Published in Frederiksborg Amts Avis on 09.10.2024.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederiksborg_Castle\", \"score\": 0.9999999995993676, \"rank\": 4.006129941468227e-10, \"text\": \"Frederiksborg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederiksborg_Castle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederiksborg_Castle\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avis_Car_Rental\", \"score\": 0.9966017685223496, \"rank\": 0.003409818831226326, \"text\": \"Avis\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avis_Car_Rental\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avis_Car_Rental\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In recent weeks, the Paris Olympics have filled the airwaves around the world.\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recent weeks\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 178}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"the airwaves\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could not wish for a better opportunity to brand your city and country.\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better opportunity\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"your city\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course, the organizers of the Paris Olympics have taken advantage of this.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a larger narrative about this year's Olympics being the most sustainable Olympics ever, the organizers highlight a number of climate initiatives that I, as Dean of Sustainability at DTU, am excited about.\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999969175412148, \"rank\": 2.2173570225270873e-06, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a larger narrative\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympics\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"the most sustainable Olympics\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"climate initiatives\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"Sustainability\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These include beds made from recycled cardboard, audience seats made from recycled plastic, the decision not to build new buildings and a 100 per cent connection to the electricity grid instead of polluting diesel generators.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beds\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled cardboard\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"audience seats\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled plastic\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"new buildings\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the electricity grid\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"diesel generators\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a great story!\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a great story\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet - it's far more complex than that.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcements from Paris have been met withcriticism from both scientists and NGOs.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992989048863, \"rank\": 7.010956899724773e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The announcements\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"withcriticism\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"both scientists\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"NGOs\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The criticism relates to the organizers' main message that the many initiatives, combined with the purchase of carbon offsets, mean that this year's Olympics will halve the climate impact compared to previous years.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers' main message\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the many initiatives\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"the purchase\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon offsets\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympics\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate impact\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"previous years\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The criticism is that this is an impenetrable claim.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"an impenetrable claim\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That buying carbon offsets cannot simply 'erase' the CO2 you emit.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"carbon offsets\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"the CO2\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that the reductions you boast about only represent an insignificant drop in the overall global carbon footprint.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reductions\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"an insignificant drop\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall global carbon footprint\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I find it annoying that initiatives that could inspire change around the world are drowned in a negative debate.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"initiatives\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"a negative debate\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It scratches credibility and leads to accusations of greenwashing.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"credibility\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"accusations\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At worst, the climate criticism of the Olympics can serve as a scare tactic for companies considering investing in more sustainable technologies.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the climate criticism\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"a scare tactic\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"companies\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"more sustainable technologies\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, why spend money on CO2 reductions if the story turns negative?\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"CO2 reductions\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At DTU, we work a lot with sustainability and how we talk about it in a fact-based way.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a fact-based way\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because it's complex.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a Centre for Absolute Sustainability, whose purpose is, through mathematics and facts, to analyze the degree of sustainability in a company or a given product by looking at the production journey from cradle to grave.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Centre\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"Absolute Sustainability\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"whose purpose\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"mathematics\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"facts\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the degree\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the production journey\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"cradle\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"grave\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The centre helps companies in Denmark and internationally to achieve absolute environmental sustainability.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.8908287306703987e-13, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The centre\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"companies\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"absolute environmental sustainability\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means that nature's tolerance limits are used as a yardstick for how much the company's products and actions can be allowed to impact the climate.\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nature's tolerance limits\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"a yardstick\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"the company's products\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"actions\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Achieving absolute sustainability is a long and demanding journey.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"absolute sustainability\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"a long and demanding journey\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A process with many steps along the way that I believe should be openly presented as inspiration for others, even if the goal has not yet been reached.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A process\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"many steps\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2547}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At DTU, for example, we are not there yet, but we still tell the world about the many initiatives we are proud of.\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2664, \"end\": 2667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"the many initiatives\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, all new infrastructure on campus is built with sustainability as a guiding principle.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2787}, {\"ngram\": \"all new infrastructure\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"campus\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"a guiding principle\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means, for example, that DTU's newly built centre for the development of climate-friendly power-to-X technologies, the Climate Challenge Laboratory, is constructed from cross-laminated timber, a renewable natural resource that requires less energy to produce than concrete and steel.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2905, \"end\": 2908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"the Climate Challenge Laboratory\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"cross-laminated timber\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"a renewable natural resource\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"less energy\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3127}, {\"ngram\": \"concrete\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3152}, {\"ngram\": \"steel\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We also explain how a light railway is being built on our campus in Lyngby, which we have used as an opportunity to expand and improve the bicycle infrastructure to promote green mobility.\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3233, \"end\": 3239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kongens_Lyngby\", \"score\": 0.9999999999768079, \"rank\": 2.3221158151831093e-11, \"text\": \"Lyngby\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kongens_Lyngby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kongens_Lyngby\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a light railway\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"our campus\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"the bicycle infrastructure\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"green mobility\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DTU also says that all facilities are available as a living laboratory where students, researchers, companies and authorities can develop and test new sustainable technologies.\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3354, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all facilities\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"a living laboratory\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"companies\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"new sustainable technologies\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, we announce that we plan to establish our own heat pump because it can reduce the climate impact by covering 30% of DTU's annual heat consumption.\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3656, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DTU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Technical_University_of_Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our own heat pump\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate impact\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"30%\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going back to the Olympics as an example, I think the organizers could have done the same.\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, they could have simply talked about the individual initiatives.\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3793}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual initiatives\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, it's not the initiatives themselves that are being criticized.\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the initiatives\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather, it's the difficult-to-understand claim that the measures, together with the purchase of carbon offsets, mean that the Paris Olympics has halved its climate impact.\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 4105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4060, \"end\": 4074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the difficult-to-understand claim\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"the measures\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 3998}, {\"ngram\": \"the purchase\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon offsets\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"its climate impact\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the maths had been presented freely for that particular claim, or not made at all, I believe the reception of the important messages would have been quite different.\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the maths\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4119}, {\"ngram\": \"that particular claim\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4171}, {\"ngram\": \"the reception\", \"from\": 4203, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"the important messages\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The climate-friendly initiatives could have served as inspiration for others and effective branding of Paris as host city.\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4380, \"end\": 4385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999992989048863, \"rank\": 7.010956899724773e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The climate-friendly initiatives\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4309}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4342}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4353}, {\"ngram\": \"effective branding\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4376}, {\"ngram\": \"host city\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, facts, honesty and transparency are essential when we talk about sustainability as a concept.\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"facts\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4416}, {\"ngram\": \"honesty\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4425}, {\"ngram\": \"transparency\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4490}, {\"ngram\": \"a concept\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, it's a waste of effort if solid work is criticized because it is decorated with green feathers that can not fly.\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a waste\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4529}, {\"ngram\": \"effort\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4539}, {\"ngram\": \"solid work\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"green feathers\", \"from\": 4597, \"to\": 4611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00ab BackVoteResults \\u00bb\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00ab BackVoteResults\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4648}]}]}"